               <p>I saw the prisoner come into the shop, when I was behind the counter; he reached down these cups and saucers from a shelf and ran away with them, directly I called out to a German; he followed him, and brought<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178004050017"></xptr>him back. I took these cups and saucers from him.</p>
               <p>- CRANE sworn.</p>
               <p>I stopped the prisoner and saw the cups taken from him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17800405-12-person174">
                  Ann
                   Hewson
               <interp inst="t17800405-12-person174" type="surname" value="Hewson"></interp>
