                     <interp inst="t17800405-12-person175" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , the constable, produced the cups and saucers in court, and they were deposed to by the Prosecutrix.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>A man asked me to take this china up the street, I do not know the name of the street, and I was to leave them at the alehouse till he came.</p>
